title: Alice in the Country of Hearts, Vol. 5
description: The NEW YORK TIMES bestselling manga continues!As the big ball approaches, everyone has an opinion on whether Alice should attend or not, and, more importantly, what kind of dress she should wear. But when Alice hears Blood's going to be there as well, she changes her mind about spending time with Wonderland's nest. The party promises to offer more than dresses and dancing in Alice in the Country of Hearts Volume 5!
author: Hoshino Soumei
